import React from 'react';
import Box from '@mui/system/Box';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import List from '@mui/material/List';
import ListItemText from '@mui/material/ListItemText';
import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import rogue from "../../pictures/Rogue.jpeg";
import cc from "../../pictures/CrookedCan.png";
import cdme from "../../pictures/CDME.jpeg";

function Experience() {
  return (
    <Grid container direction="column" spacing={0}>
        <Grid item>
            <Paper variant="elevation" elevation={10} sx={{backgroundColor: "#F7F4EA", borderRadius: "10px"}} className="paper">
                <Grid container direction="row" alignItems="center" spacing={2} className="grid">
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Box
                            component="img"
                            sx={{maxWidth: { xs: 350, md: 250 }}}
                            src={rogue} 
                            alt="Rogue Fitness" 
                        />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Typography component="h1" className="title">Rogue Fitness</Typography>
                        <Typography component="h3" className="subtitle">Product Design Engineer</Typography>
                        <List>
                            <ListItemText primary="GPA" secondary="it's a gpa." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Outline of Program" secondary="the program is of such information and learning." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Class Highlights" secondary="classes i've taken are of such variety" />
                        </List>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
            <Paper variant="elevation" elevation={10} sx={{backgroundColor: "#F7F4EA", borderRadius: "10px"}} className="paper">
                <Grid container direction="row" alignItems="center" spacing={2} className="grid">
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Box
                            component="img"
                            sx={{maxWidth: { xs: 350, md: 250 }}}
                            src={cc} 
                            alt="Crooked Can" 
                        />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Typography component="h1" className="title">Crooked Can</Typography>
                        <Typography component="h3" className="subtitle">Bartender</Typography>
                        <List>
                            <ListItemText primary="GPA" secondary="it's a gpa." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Outline of Program" secondary="the program is of such information and learning." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Class Highlights" secondary="classes i've taken are of such variety" />
                        </List>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item>
            <Paper variant="elevation" elevation={10} sx={{backgroundColor: "#F7F4EA", borderRadius: "10px"}} className="paper">
                <Grid container direction="row" alignItems="center" spacing={2} className="grid">
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Box
                            component="img"
                            sx={{maxWidth: { xs: 350, md: 250 }}}
                            src={cdme} 
                            alt="CDME" 
                        />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <Typography component="h1" className="title">Center for Design and Manufacturing Excellence</Typography>
                        <Typography component="h3" className="subtitle">Undergraduate Engineering Assisstant</Typography>
                        <List>
                            <ListItemText primary="GPA" secondary="it's a gpa." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Outline of Program" secondary="the program is of such information and learning." />
                            <ListItemText primary="Class Highlights" secondary="classes i've taken are of such variety" />
                        </List>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
}

export default Experience;
